1 Section 1(g). 1. "Cumulative sales tax rate" as used
2 in section 1(i) of this article shall mean the rate of the
3 state sales tax, levied and imposed under section 1(e), plus
4 the rate of the taxes imposed by article IV, sections 43(a)
5 and 47(a), as calculated in section 1(h), plus the rate of
